LIVE Transfer Talk: PSG's Lookman doubt opens way for Arsenal

Atalanta's Ademola Lookman hopes of joining Paris-Saint Germain are set to be dashed, but will Arsenal step in? Transfer Talk is LIVE with the latest.

Rajan Hothi

Ben Shelton shouts out brother at US Open after 1st-round win

Ben Shelton defeats Dominic Thiem in straight sets to progress to the second round of the US Open and shouts out his brother following the match.
